examples.en: It boils down to a question of priorities.
Flight aerodynamics were one of the top priorities in the design.
You need to reorder your priorities.
A good car is high on my list of priorities.
I would place health quite high on my list of priorities.
She decided to go to the party instead of studying? Where are her priorities?
Proper food and sleep should overweigh all-night partying in your priorities.
The customer is high on our list of priorities.
They kept a firm grip on the two top priorities.
Our top priorities must be profit and commercial growth.
Getting the car fixed is number one on my list of priorities.
Their purpose is to elevate AIDS to the top of government priorities.
